wikipedia_page.main: Oliver Courtenay Soames (born 27 October 1995) is an English cricketer who played for Hampshire. He made his first-class debut on 1 April 2018 for Loughborough MCCU against Sussex as part of the Marylebone Cricket Club University fixtures. He made his Hampshire debut against Worcestershire in the County Championship on 4 September 2018. Soames was released by Hampshire ahead of the 2021 County Championship.
